%--------------COMPILE INSTRUCTION---------------------------------
g++ -O2 -o deryu deryu.cpp
%------------------------------------------------------------------

%--------------Brief Intro to Our Algo.----------------------------
We use a determinized UCT when the number of the cards in hands are large.
When the hands becomes smaller, we randomize opponent's hands and use the 
alpha-beta pruning to compute the expected value of all possible moves, and 
then select the move with the largest expected value.
%------------------------------------------------------------------
